config.desc_defaultFoodLevel: Starting food level e.g. beginning a new game or died respawning... This is not the upper limit of food level
config.desc_guiStarving: GUI color or style used when the player is starving.
config.desc_guiNormal: GUI color or style used when the player is in a normal state.
config.desc_guiOvereating: GUI color or style used when the player is overeating.
config.desc_threshold: Thresholds used for food level stages.
config.desc_thresholdMin: Minimum threshold before entering the starving stage.
config.desc_thresholdLow: Low threshold defining early hunger effects.
config.desc_thresholdMid: Mid threshold defining moderate hunger effects.
config.desc_thresholdMidpointHighMax: Useless, Hit about the Midpoint between high and maximum thresholds.
config.desc_thresholdMax: Maximum threshold before severe overeating effects.
config.desc_thresholdEffect: Effect applied when crossing a threshold. Short or long is time about player stay in that state.
config.desc_threshold_Min_ShortEffectId: Effect ID applied after short time beyond the threshold.
config.desc_threshold_Min_LongEffectId: Effect ID applied after long time beyond the threshold.
config.desc_thresholdMin_Low_EffectId: Effect ID applied beyond the threshold.
config.desc_thresholdHigh_ShortEffectId: Effect ID applied after short time beyond the threshold.
config.desc_thresholdHigh_LongEffectId: Effect ID applied after long time beyond the threshold.
config.desc_thresholdHigh_Max_ShortEffec: Effect ID applied after short time beyond the threshold.
config.desc_thresholdHigh_Max_LongEffect: Effect ID applied after long time beyond the threshold.
config.desc_nutritionModifierSystem: Multiplier system applied to every nutrition gained from food. Without this, many foods can only give up to 20 food level. Cause vanilla version food level has maximum of 20
config.desc_nutritionModifierEnabled: Whether the nutrition modifier is enabled.
config.desc_nutritionRandomModifierEnabl: Whether random nutrition modification is enabled.
config.desc_saturationRandomization: Randomization system applied to saturation. Applied to all saturation actions
config.desc_decreaseFoodLevelOverTime: Food level decreaseing system, decrease over time.
config.desc_decreaseFoodLevelOverTimeEna: Whether food level decreases over time.
config.desc_decreaseFoodLevelBaseTicks: Base tick interval for decreasing food level.
config.desc_decreaseFoodLevelBaseAmounts: Base amount of food level lost.
config.desc_randomDecreaseFoodLevelEnabl: The time, whether randomize time interval.
config.desc_randomDecreaseFoodLevelMinMu: Minimum multiplier for random food level decrease.
config.desc_randomDecreaseFoodLevelMaxMu: Maximum multiplier for random food level decrease.
config.desc_decreaseRandomFoodLevelEnabl: The food level, whether randomize food level amounts.
config.desc_decreaseFoodLevelMinMultipli: Minimum multiplier for decreasing food level.
config.desc_decreaseFoodLevelMaxMultipli: Maximum multiplier for decreasing food level.
config.desc_exhaustionModifierEnabled: Whether the exhaustion multiplier is enabled.
config.desc_exhaustionCap: Maximum exhaustion value before triggering hunger loss.
config.desc_addExhaustionOverTime: Base amount of exhaustion added over time.
config.desc_addExhaustionBaseTicks: Base tick interval for adding exhaustion.
config.desc_randomAddExhaustionEnabled: The time, whether randomize time interval.
config.desc_randomAddExhaustionMinMultip: Minimum multiplier for random exhaustion increase.
config.desc_randomAddExhaustionMaxMultip: Maximum multiplier for random exhaustion increase.
config.desc_addRandomExhaustionEnabled: The exhaustion, whether randomize exhaustion amounts.
config.desc_addPerTickDamage: Damage syastem applied per tick. Using the DamageType.
config.desc_damageStarvingDamageTypeId: Damage type ID used when starving.
config.desc_damageOvereatingDamageTypeId: Damage type ID used when overeating.
config.desc_addPerTickRealDamage: Real damage syastem applied per tick. By directly decreasing player's Health
config.desc_addPerTickRealDamageEnabled: Whether per-tick real damage is enabled.
config.desc_realDamageStarvingAmounts: Real damage amount applied when starving.
config.desc_realDamageOvereatingAmounts: Real damage amount applied when overeating.
